OL,3,CWill you get money back as water firms
OL,4,Cordered to return #158m to customers?
OL,6,FNot one water company achieved Ofwat's
OL,7,Ftop category of "leading", as ITV
OL,8,FNews' Business Editor Joel Hills report
OL,10,FWater firms have been ordered to pay
OL,11,F#157.6 million back to customers after
OL,12,Fmissing key targets on pollution,
OL,13,Fleaks, supply interruptions and
OL,14,Ffalling customer satisfaction.
OL,16,FOfwat, the water regulator, has judged
OL,17,Feach of the water companies and found
OL,18,Fthat none met the criteria for their
OL,19,Ftop category of "leading".
