OL,6,FAnglian Water, Welsh Water and
OL,7,FSouthern Water fell into its lowest
OL,8,Fcategory of "lagging", while the
OL,9,Fremaining 10 were awarded an "average"
OL,10,Frating.
OL,12,FBosses at the regulator judge the
OL,13,Fperformance of water firms each year
OL,14,Fagainst "stretching targets" they set
OL,15,Fin 2019 for a five-year period until
OL,16,F2025.
OL,18,FFailure to meet those targets results
OL,19,Fin Ofwat restricting the amount of
OL,20,Fmoney they can take from customers.
