OL,6,FCustomers won't need to chase the
OL,7,Fmoney owed by water firms, their bills
OL,8,Fwill instead be amended to reflect the
OL,9,Fdecision made by the water regulator.
OL,11,FOfwat has said the figures are
OL,12,Fprovisional until it completes a
OL,13,Freview process in December - the exact
OL,14,Famount that will be returned to
OL,15,Fcustomers will also be finalised then.
