OL,6,F"It is clear that companies need to
OL,7,Fchange and that has to start with
OL,8,Faddressing issues of culture and
OL,9,Fleadership. Too often we hear that
OL,10,Fweather, third parties or external
OL,11,Ffactors are blamed for shortcomings.
OL,13,F"Companies must implement actions now
OL,14,Fto improve performance, be more
OL,15,Fdynamic, agile and on the front foot
OL,16,Fof issues. And not wait until the
OL,17,Fgovernment or regulators tell them to
OL,18,Fact.
