OL,6,FSome water utilities are also creaking
OL,7,Funder high levels of debt or face
OL,8,Fcriticism over dividends to
OL,9,Fshareholders and executive bonuses.
OL,11,FLabour has said it wants the sector to
OL,12,Freduce spills and has even proposed
OL,13,Fsweeping new laws which could see
OL,14,Fbosses face up to two years in jail if
OL,15,Fthey obstruct regulators.
OL,17,FOn Monday, a report from the
OL,18,FEnvironment Agency found that almost a
OL,19,Ffifth of water supplies are being lost
OL,20,Fthrough leaks before they reach
OL,21,Fcustomers' taps.
